44 class PartialThirdbodyEffs
45 {
46 public:
47 
48  PartialThirdbodyEffs(
49  const size_t rxn, const std::vector<std::pair<int, double> >& effs)
50  : m_rxn(rxn), m_effs(effs)
51  { }
52 
53  inline void multiplyEfficiencies(
54  double sum, const double* const p_s, double* const p_r) const
55  {
56  std::vector<std::pair<int, double> >::const_iterator iter;
57  for (iter = m_effs.begin(); iter != m_effs.end(); ++iter)
58  sum += p_s[iter->first] * iter->second;
59  p_r[m_rxn] *= sum;
60  }
61 
62 private:
63 
64  size_t m_rxn;
65  std::vector<std::pair<int, double> > m_effs;
66 
67 }; // class PartialThirdbodyEffs

74 class ThirdbodyManager
75 {
76 public:
77 
81  ThirdbodyManager(const size_t ns, const bool electrons)
82  : m_ns(ns), m_offset(electrons ? 1 : 0)
83  { }
84 
88  void addReaction(
89  const size_t rxn, const std::vector<std::pair<int, double> > effs)
90  {
91  std::vector<std::pair<int, double> > partial_effs;
92  std::vector<std::pair<int, double> >::const_iterator iter;
93 
94  for (iter = effs.begin(); iter != effs.end(); ++iter) {
95  if (iter->second != 1.0)
96  partial_effs.push_back(
97  std::make_pair(iter->first, iter->second - 1.0));
98  }
99 
100  m_effs.push_back(PartialThirdbodyEffs(rxn, partial_effs));
101  }
102 
108  void multiplyThirdbodies(const double* const p_s, double* const p_r) const
109  {
110  double sum = std::accumulate(p_s+m_offset, p_s+m_ns, 0.0);
111 
112  std::vector<PartialThirdbodyEffs>::const_iterator iter = m_effs.begin();
113  for ( ; iter != m_effs.end(); ++iter)
114  iter->multiplyEfficiencies(sum, p_s, p_r);
115  }
116 
117 private:
118 
119  const size_t m_ns;
120  const size_t m_offset;
121  std::vector<PartialThirdbodyEffs> m_effs;
122 
123 }; // class ThirdbodyManager
